subtitle: Rumor has it that Homa Abedine kept deleted e-mails about Hillary Clinton in a volume called Life Insurance, and made a deal with the FBI for them.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Homa Abedine kept an e-mail deleted from Hillary Clinton in a folder marked "Life Insurance" and made a deal with the FBI.
